Credit for this amazing animation goes to Ilya Pavlov: https://lottiefiles.com/MiLushin  
You can his original here: https://lottiefiles.com/8586-rocket-in-space

I modified the original to have a transparent background.  The original has a white vignette shape that makes the stars fade as they approach the edges.  It works great as long as it's on a transparent background, but can look funny against darker backgrounds. 

I removed the vignette and animated the opacity of each background element, which manages to achieve the same effect while allowing for alternate background colors.
